30:44.042 --> 30:57.589 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: Now, for a closer
look at the
man who could shape the
conservative direction

30:57.622 --> 31:01.226 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
