33:44.322 --> 33:48.693 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NINA TOTENBERG, NPR: This was a
dissent that
Gorsuch authored, and he was
vindicated by

33:48.727 --> 33:51.529 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
