34:40.278 --> 34:41.446 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
on this?

34:41.479 --> 34:43.248 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARCIA COYLE, "The National Law
Journal":
Absolutely.

34:43.281 --> 34:46.451 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
