their religious
beliefs.

35:18.817 --> 35:27.759 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think, as Nina just said,
Judge Gorsuch's
dissent here does give some
concern to these

35:27.792 --> 35:33.932 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
civil rights organizations as to
how far you
can take not only his comments,
but the Supreme

35:33.965 --> 35:35.467 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Court's Hobby Lobby decision.

35:35.500 --> 35:39.270 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: Everybody is
