41:57.815 --> 41:58.916 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in rural Ghana.

41:58.950 --> 42:00.752 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

42:00.785 --> 42:05.890 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KWAKU POKU ASANTE: The women who
do commercial
cooking with the traditional
cookstoves, they

42:05.923 --> 42:10.461 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
