51:46.904 --> 51:49.907 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that's one of the things
that we're talking
about here with cervical cancer
screening

51:49.940 --> 51:52.810 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
is, we have got to make sure
that these preventative
services are there.

